messages.message: @jtau / @Ashwin,  C1 would like to have a release of 22.01 with the Ubuntu Base OS image updated to a current release and not the EOL version. Please let us know if you would have an ETA on when it would be ready to ship for IB 22.01. @shiqi can fill in for more context regarding the Customer call from today morning.
We are working on backporting the Ubuntu upgrade to 22.01 today, will keep you updated as we go
